# Pin fixed host ports so `ssh -L 3333:localhost:3333 dev-box` keeps working across
# container restarts (without this, outpost publishes each EXPOSE'd port to a NEW
# dynamic host port every restart). One container port per line; host port = same,
# or use "container:host" to remap. Check the live mapping: outpost ports <name>
3333        # API
4322        # admin (Vite)
4323        # web (Astro)
# 4322:14322  # example remap: container 4322 -> host 14322
